l part except at very low\ntemperatures.There are two experimental signatures of IM on $\\kappa_{yx}$: A\nnon-monotonic temperature dependence and a sign change as a function of\ntemperature depending on the scattering process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 2 Nov 2019 13:18:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-05"}
